    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle offers an accessible entry point for anyone needing straightforward transportation or a solid project candidate. It shows its age and wear, but presents an opportunity for the right buyer to get into a vehicle at a very approachable price. A practical value-focused choice being offered with clear, honest positioning.",
