    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little car with plenty of life left for the right buyer. It\u2019s not perfect and shows its age, but it starts, runs, and could make a handy cheap runabout, first project, or parts donor depending on what you need. If you\u2019re after something affordable and straightforward, this one could be well worth a look.",
      "price": 5400.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly car with a strong-running engine, smooth-shifting drivetrain, and the kind of straightforward mechanical feel that makes it a great daily, backup car, or weekend project. It shows cosmetic wear consistent with age and use, but it remains a practical, capable driver with good bones and plenty of serviceable life left for the next owner. If you want affordable transportation with character and real potential, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
