      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A true underdog with old-school charm, this car has the kind of honest character you can feel the moment you see it. It\u2019s the perfect candidate for someone who appreciates a budget-friendly ride with plenty of story left to tell\u2014whether you need a practical daily, a weekend project, or just a set of wheels with grit and soul. There\u2019s a lot of value here for the right buyer: affordable entry point, unmistakable personality, and the chance to make it your own.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next owner, this vehicle offers dependable basic transportation at an easy entry price. It shows its age cosmetically and mechanically, but for the right buyer it represents a practical opportunity for a work car, first car, or project. Priced with its overall condition in mind, it delivers straightforward value for someone who wants affordability above all else.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left to give? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable transportation without spending a fortune. It\u2019s got the kind of character you expect from a well-used vehicle, and with a little TLC it could make a great daily driver, commuter, or first car. If you want something honest, practical, and easy on the wallet, this one is definitely worth a look.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Tough, honest driver with solid project appeal and plenty of usable life for the right buyer. The powertrain pulls through the rev range, the chassis feels planted, and it has the kind of straightforward mechanical layout that makes it a great budget entry, shop truck, or weekend fixer. Not a showpiece, but it has character, presence, and the bones of a dependable runner with room for improvement. If you want an affordable vehicle you can drive, wrench on, and gradually sort to your taste, this one makes a compelling case.",
